=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Overviews_Operators_ex46 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_bright gritty sound, with noise oscillator character around 51 Hz, featuring slow attack and percussive envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with highpass character, and spectrally dense.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: slow
  brightness: very_bright
  crest_factor_db: percussive
  envelope_flatness: very_dynamic
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: gritty
  spectral_complexity_mean: dense
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: highpass
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 51.4651
  harmonic_decay_rate: -0.0067
  harmonic_regularity: 0.0284
  pitch_clarity: 12.4254
  inharmonicity: 0.0347
  type: noise
[filter]
  spectral_slope: 0.0143
  resonance_freq: 0.0000

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: Operators Example 46
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Overviews/Operators.html
// Tags: Operators, Overviews
// ---
// --- Example 46 ---
{ WhiteNoise.ar.amclip(FSinOsc.kr(1,0.2)) }.play; // makes a sine envelope
